Deg [[Tasengama|tsengama]], '''Tazzla taslullit''' d [[tazzla]] deg wanda i d-tettili deg-s [[tafasa tamussayt|tfasa tamussayt]] i kra n tfekka tegda [[tafasa tanezmart|tafasa-ines tanudebt]], ayen yennumken d akken tanafa-nsent tegda 0, anecta yennumk daɣen d akken tazzla i d-tekkes tfekka ur telli deg tjumma ur telli deg [[timezzit|tmezzit]] tumdilt. Ma d ass mi ara ad tembiwel tfekka s tazzla n trewla w ad ittaggeg (ad ittbeɛɛid) ɣef [[Tagnit|tegnit]] imur-nni ad islukkuz w ad iṭɣaray maca ur yettawaṭ ara, ayen yennumken d akken tazzla ur tettuɣal ara d 0, neɣ ma yella teffeɣ tazzla n trewla i tikkelt tamezwarut anecta ur iserri ara (ur yettuḥwaj ara) ɣer usemdu n tmerniwt n tdusi n udemmer ɣef tfekka alamma yesmed (ikemmel) tarewla-ines.<br/>
D imezdi daɣen usenmel d tbadut n tazzla taslullit d akken-it d tazzla yettwatteen i trewla ɣef yiger n [[Taldayt|teldayt]]. Azamul-is iga d <math>v_e</math> tettwasiden s wassaɣ:
:<math>v_e = \sqrt{\frac{2 \cdot G \cdot M}{r}}</math>
Anda <math>G</math> d [[Timezgit taldayant|timezgit taldayant tamatut]] (6.67408 × 10<sup>−11</sup> m<sup>3</sup> kg<sup>−1</sup> [[tasint|t]]<sup>−2</sup> ), <math>M</math> ia d takura n [[itrikli|umtiweg]], ma d <math>r</math> d azen-kdu-ines.
* Ad nessegri deg usaduf-a d akken tazzla n teslullit n kra n tfekka ur tegguni ara ɣef [[takura|tkura-ines]] maca tegguni kan ɣef tkura n umtiweg.

Deg yiger n teldayt n [[tagnit|tegnit]], i wakken kra n tfekka ad teǧǧ tagnit w ad terwel fellas tesri tazzla taslullit <math>v_{e}</math> yegdan azal n 11,2 km/[[tasint|t]], maca tarewla ɣef teldayt n [[tafukt|tfukt]] d ttwaffɣa seg [[udus anafuk|wudus anafuk]] seg yiwen n wazag yesri ɣer tazzla taslullit yegdan 42.1 km/t

Mi ara ad tili tuzzla i d-ittunefken tugar tazzla n trewla, imir-nni tafekka ad teṭɣar seg <math>\upsilon\infty</math> hypebrolic excess speed, s unect n tagda ayi:

<math>v\infty=v^2-ve</math>

